posts.post_title: FS: T216 People's Tobacco, incl. HOFers
posts.post_content:
Hi all, I am looking to sell my T216 People’s Tobacco cards.  I am accepting PayPal only for these.  Prices are net to me, so please add 3% for regular PayPal.  Domestic shipping is on me.  Shipping to other countries, I will work with you on price.

Additional scans available on request.  Thanks, and feel free to e-mail any questions: [URL="skeltone@rocketmail.com"]skeltone@rocketmail.com[/URL].

First commitment to buy will go before ongoing negotiations.

Chief Bender White Cap Baltimore Fed $
Al Bridwell batting $
John McGraw MG Large Print [STRIKE][STRIKE]$500[/STRIKE][/STRIKE]Sold
Jeff Sweeney $
Joe Tinker Batting [STRIKE]$500[/STRIKE]Chicago Nat'l 
Sold

Bob Bescher St. Louis Fed[strike] $250[/strike]Sold
Mickey Doolan Phila Nat. [strike]$100[/strike]Sold

Hans Lobert New York Nat'l [strike]$375[/strike]Sold
George McQuillan [strike]$200[/strike]Sold
Joe Tinker Portrait [strike]$350[/strike]Sold
